[
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛說開覺自性般若波羅蜜多",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0861c09_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "經卷第四",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0861c10_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "西天譯經三藏朝散大夫試光祿卿",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0861c12_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "傳梵大師賜紫沙門臣法護等",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0861c13_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "奉　詔譯",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0861c14_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0861c15_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩摩訶薩於色法中，應當了知有五種相，親近善知識。",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0861c15_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等為五？",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0861c16_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一、聽受親近，二、承事作用學法親近，三、修行進向親近，四、親近，五、大親近。",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0861c16_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0861c18_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "受、想、行、識亦復如是。",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0861c18_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩摩訶薩於識法中，應當了知有五種相，親近善知識。",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0861c19_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等為五，一、聽受親近，二、承事作用學法親近，三、修行進向親近，四、親近，五、大親近。",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0861c20_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是親近善知識時，菩薩摩訶薩以解脫方便而為攝受，即能生多福，疾成阿耨多羅三藐三菩提果。",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0861c22_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0861c25_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩摩訶薩於色法中，應當了知有五種相，供養如來。",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0861c25_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等為五？",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0861c26_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一、種種讚歎恭信供養，二、以清淨利養恭信供養，三、修行進向供養，四、供養，五、大供養。",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0861c26_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0861c28_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "受、想、行、識亦復如是。",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0861c28_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩摩訶薩於識法中，應當了知有五種相，供養如來。",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0861c29_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等為五？",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0862a01_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一、種種讚歎恭信供養，二、以清淨利養恭信供養，三、修行進向供養，四、供養，五、大供養。",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0862a01_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0862a03_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩摩訶薩若能如是供養如來，如理相應者，即得無邊世界諸佛菩薩共所稱讚，亦得世間天、人、阿修羅等利養供給，成熟無量無邊眾生，嚴淨佛土，疾成阿耨多羅三藐三菩提果。",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0862a04_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0862a09_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩摩訶薩於色法中，能與布施波羅蜜多如理相應者，若修有相施，亦速圓滿布施波羅蜜多；若修無相施，亦速圓滿布施波羅蜜多。",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0862a09_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0862a12_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何是菩薩摩訶薩於色法中，修有相施或無相施？",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0862a12_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0862a13_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若菩薩摩訶薩於色法中修行布施求解脫時，有所解脫布施可得，有能解脫布施可得，如是修者，當知是菩薩摩訶薩於色法中修有相施。",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0862a13_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若菩薩摩訶薩於色法中，修行布施求解脫時，無所解脫布施可得，無能解脫布施可得。",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0862a17_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0862a19_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "謂色自性無所得故，本性無所得故；觀諸如來亦無所得，本性無所得故。",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0862a19_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
