    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩摩訶薩於色法中，應當了知空三摩地。",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0864a01_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0864a02_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何是色中空三摩地？",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0864a02_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩摩訶薩謂於色中觀無性空，性空亦然，本性空亦然。",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0864a03_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸所緣事，皆當安住心一境性，此即是為色中空三摩地。",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0864a04_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0864a05_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩摩訶薩若於色中，如是如實了知空三摩地已，受，想，行，識亦復如是。",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0864a05_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0864a08_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩摩訶薩於色法中，應當了知無相三摩地。",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0864a08_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0864a09_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何是色中無相三摩地？",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0864a09_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩摩訶薩謂於色中觀無性空，性空亦然，本性空亦然。",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0864a10_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若能如是，諸作意滅，即於色中觀無性相，有性相亦然，有性無性相亦然。",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0864a11_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是乃得無性相離識隨逐，有性相亦然，離識隨逐，有性無性相亦然，離識隨逐。",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0864a13_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "故能安住心一境性，此即是為色中無相三摩地。",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0864a14_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0864a16_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
