        "source_sentence": "一、不實義，二、破壞義，三、有垢無垢義。",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0864a28_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0864a29_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "受、想、行、識亦復如是，菩薩摩訶薩應當了知有三種義諸行無常。",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0864a29_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0864b03_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩摩訶薩於色法中，應當了知有三種義諸行是苦。",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0864b03_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等為三？",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0864b04_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一、無取著義，二、三種相義，三、相續義。",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0864b04_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0864b05_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "受、想、行、識亦復如是，菩薩摩訶薩應當了知有三種義諸行是苦。",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0864b05_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0864b08_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩摩訶薩於色法中，應當了知有三種義諸法無我。",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0864b08_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等為三？",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0864b09_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一、無性無我義，二、有性無性無我義，三、本性清淨無我義。",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0864b09_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0864b11_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "受、想、行、識亦復如是，菩薩摩訶薩應當了知有三種義諸法無我。",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0864b11_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0864b13_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩摩訶薩於色法中，應當了知有三種義涅槃寂靜。",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0864b13_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等為三。",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0864b14_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一、色中無性畢竟寂靜義，二、有性無性寂靜義，三、本性清淨寂靜義。",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0864b14_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0864b16_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "受、想、行、識亦復如是，菩薩摩訶薩應當了知有三種義涅槃寂靜。」",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0864b16_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛說此經已，諸菩薩摩訶薩，尊者須菩提，及諸苾芻、苾芻尼、優婆塞、優婆夷，一切世間天、人、阿修羅、乾闥婆等，聞佛所說，皆大歡喜，信受奉行。",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0864b17_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛說開覺自性般若波羅蜜多經卷第四",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0864b22_0",
